<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Login Details</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        body { 
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif; 
            line-height: 1.6; 
            color: #333; 
            max-width: 600px; 
            min-width: 500px;
            margin: 0 auto; 
            padding: 20px; 
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 200px; 
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            display: block;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white !important;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: #777;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .details-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .details-table td {
            padding: 8px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .details-table td.label {
            font-weight: bold;
            width: 150px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear @Model.Name,</p>
            
            <p>Your account has been registered. Below are your login details:</p>
            
            <table class="details-table">
                <tr>
                    <td class="label">Email:</td>
                    <td>@Model.Email</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="label">Password:</td>
                    <td>@Model.Password</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="label">Portal Link:</td>
                    <td><a href="@Model.PortalUrl">@Model.PortalUrl</a></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            
            <p>Please log in using the above credentials. For security, we recommend changing your password after your first login.</p>
            
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our support team at @Model.SupportEmail.</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>
            The MCC Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; @DateTime.Now.Year MCC. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>